import { StyleSheet } from 'react-native';
import Constants from 'expo-constants';

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    background: {
        flex: 1,
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: "center",
        backgroundColor: '#FFF',
        paddingTop: Constants.statusBarHeight + 20,
    },
    input: {
        backgroundColor: '#ffff',
        width: 280,
        marginBottom: 15,
        borderColor: '#27b341',
        color: '#333',
        fontSize: 17,
        borderRadius: 15,
        padding: 10,
        borderRightWidth: 3,
        borderLeftWidth: 3,
        borderTopWidth: 2,
        borderBottomWidth: 2,
    },

    btnSalvar: {
        width: 70,
        height: 70,
        backgroundColor: '#2AB940',
        borderRadius: 70 / 2,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
        right: 99,
    },
    
    btnCancelar: {
        width: 70,
        height: 70,
        backgroundColor: '#2AB940',
        borderRadius: 70 / 2,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center',
        left: 99
    },

    viewOrientada: {
        alignItems: 'flex-start'
        
    },

    inputOrient: {
        backgroundColor: '#ffff',
        width: 200,
        marginBottom: 15,
        borderColor: '#27b341',
        color: '#333',
        fontSize: 17,
        borderRadius: 15,
        padding: 10,
        borderRightWidth: 3,
        borderLeftWidth: 3,
        borderTopWidth: 2,
        borderBottomWidth: 2,
        alignItems: 'flex-start'
    },

    inputOrient2: {
        backgroundColor: '#ffff',
        width: 75,
        marginLeft: 10,
        marginBottom: 15,
        borderColor: '#27b341',
        color: '#333',
        fontSize: 17,
        borderRadius: 15,
        padding: 10,
        borderRightWidth: 3,
        borderLeftWidth: 3,
        borderTopWidth: 2,
        borderBottomWidth: 2,
        alignItems: 'flex-start'
    },

    action: {
        flexDirection: "row",

    },

    text: {
        color: "#333333"
    },

})

export default styles;
